        <NCI_Definition rdf:datatype="&xsd;string">Inherited disorders involving abnormalities of red blood cell function, structure, or production. Some diseases in this group may be associated with bone marrow failure, neutropenia, and/or thrombocytopenia.</NCI_Definition>
