        <ID rdf:datatype="&xsd;string">C34478</ID>
        <NCI_PT rdf:datatype="&xsd;string">Chronic Pulmonary Heart Disease</NCI_PT>
        <NCI_Definition rdf:datatype="&xsd;string">Heart disease which occurs as a result of a primary pulmonary disease. Cor pulmonale most often manifests as right ventricular hypertrophy; it can also lead to right ventricular failure.</NCI_Definition>
