        <SYN rdf:datatype="&xsd;string"></SYN>
        <NCI_Definition rdf:datatype="&xsd;string">A relatively painless, irregular tightening sensation felt by the pregnant mother over the abdomen after the 28th week of pregnancy, that lasts about a minute each time</NCI_Definition>
