        <SYN rdf:datatype="&xsd;string"></SYN>
        <NCI_Definition rdf:datatype="&xsd;string">A person who belongs to the sex that normally produces ova. The term is used to indicate biological sex distinctions, or cultural gender role distinctions, or both.</NCI_Definition>
