        <SYN rdf:datatype="&xsd;string"></SYN>
        <NCI_Definition rdf:datatype="&xsd;string">A type of abortion where the product of conception is accessed through a surgical incision on the corpus uteri intended to terminate the pregnancy.</NCI_Definition>
