        <SYN rdf:datatype="&xsd;string"></SYN>
        <NCI_Definition rdf:datatype="&xsd;string">A record of a patient&apos;s background regarding health and the occurrence of disease events of the individual. In addition, personal medical history may be a variable in epidemiologic studies.</NCI_Definition>
