        <SYN rdf:datatype="&xsd;string"></SYN>
        <NCI_Definition rdf:datatype="&xsd;string">An abnormal situation in utero, when there is increased pressure on the umbilical cord, which constricts blood supply to the fetus.</NCI_Definition>
