        <NCI_Definition rdf:datatype="&xsd;string">Paralysis of the recurrent laryngeal nerve. Causes include surgical and non-surgical traumas, neoplasms (e.g., lung carcinoma), and inflammatory neuritis.</NCI_Definition>
